{"tid":1496131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩咗Twitter幾日嘅手足，有冇發覺Twitter比FB/IG更informative同有安全感","createTime":"2019-08-22T11:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T17:08:45.000Z","uid":11703,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1475db936dce9fa34784ebb8f78b30ea537ad20f","tid":1496131,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:15:14.000Z","msg":"首先Twitter本身就係一個討論區+社交圈子嘅混合物<br />\n用假名嘅風氣比FB/IG更普遍<br />\n半真半假嘅身分令你講嘢更放更安心<br />\n<br />\n因為假名多，少好多冇營養嘅旅行/食物appeal自己嘅圖<br />\n反而更鼓勵你tweet多啲同睇多啲你本身有興趣嘅嘢<br />\n未必一定係反送中之類嘅時政tweet<br />\n可以係你個人嘅興趣<br />\n<br />\n運用番twitter hashtag同retweet嘅mechanism<br />\n好多志同道合嘅人會睇到你啲嘢<br />\n<br />\nTwitter retweet嘅風氣係遠比FB嘅forward高<br />\n因為佢比FB有更強嘅trending概念<br />\n<br />\nFB嚟嚟去去都係你圈子內嘅人like你啲嘢<br />\n但twitter好多人用假名, 佢係更鼓勵三五識七嘅人去like同retweet<br />\n同埋twitter比fb/ig更易轉account<br />\n成件事係好addictive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0940bff24ea7d52541a4ff200679b6c615a6de","tid":1496131,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a824e4313137f2a590a88a7279f457c2f1bc28c0","tid":1496131,"uid":11703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"快啲玩twitter <br />\n拉埋朋友/女朋友一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae883bf5e925eb949554f3a228d71523fe5ce99","tid":1496131,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a2ceb068a769332abe32f6c489faca0da95efe","tid":1496131,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ho